text: Marie-Paule Van Eyck (born 22 June 1951) is a Belgian fencer. She competed in the women's individual foil event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. Her daughter, Émilie Heymans, was also an Olympic athlete representing Canada in diving. == References == Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Belgium Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:People from Frameries Category:Belgian emigrants to Canada
